### Other admissibility and selection criteria
Foreign nationals eligible under this public policy are subject to all other legislative obligations and admissibility and selection criteria not exempted under this, or another, public policy.

## Effective date and expiration
This public policy takes effect forty-five calendar days after it is signed and expires on December 31, 2024.
This public policy replaces the Temporary Public Policy to exempt certain permanent residence applicants from work permit requirements signed on July 4, 2021 on the date that this public policy takes effect.
This public policy applies to pending applications for a work permit made under the Temporary Public Policy to exempt certain permanent residence applicants from work permit requirements signed on July 4, 2021, on the date that this public policy takes effect and to applications received on or after the date that this public policy takes effect.
